  ## href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonRDS/latest/UserGuide/UsingWithRDS.IAMDBAuth.html"> IAM Database Authentication for MySQL and PostgreSQL</a> in the <i>Amazon RDS User Guide.</i> </p>
  ##   DBSecurityGroups: JArray
